name: THINK
description:
Ruben Lim, 2021

The pleasure of being overwhelmed with information and having them click into place is a very specific feeling that I enjoy. I want to recreate that feeling with READ / THINK. A moment that happens in your head — the gathering of information, processing them, and fitting them into a narrative that you’ve built into your head. All very intimate and all very quick. 

Please visit www.pinktank.art for more information.
